%% Diagram: Write Policy Comparison
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Cache
    participant Store as Backing Store

    Note over App,Store: Write-Through - synchronous to both
    App->>Cache: write k v
    Cache->>Store: write k v
    Store-->>Cache: ok
    Cache-->>App: ok

    Note over App,Store: Write-Back - cache acks, store flushed later
    App->>Cache: write k v
    Cache-->>App: ok
    Cache->>Store: async flush, batched
    Store-->>Cache: ok

    Note over App,Store: Write-Around - bypass cache, populate on read
    App->>Store: write k v
    Store-->>App: ok
    App->>Cache: read k later
    Cache-->>App: miss
    App->>Store: read k
    Store-->>App: v
    App->>Cache: set k v
